biotools.summary:
a database of hydrogen/deuterium exchange data on protein folding and stability.

There are 57 entries in Start2Fold as of Aug. 30, 2020. We welcome additional data submissions! Please fill in and send the template below to Wim Vranken: XML template.

If you have any questions or suggestions regarding the database, the content or the submission procedure, please contact us by sending a message here.

The database of hydrogen/deuterium exchange data on protein folding and stability.
